data.description: A 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom gem located minutes from Ingram park mall and Holmes High school. This home has a flow anyone can enjoy, perfect for family gatherings because of the huge family/game room that offers an oversized brick fireplace & high ceilings that extend to the kitchen/dining area giving it a big and spacious feel. Granite counter top island with bar stool seating, white cabinets with a nice white back splash, & a brick wall as the divide from the living room giving the home some character & charm. Ceramic tile through the entire home, 2 car garage, and 2 covered patios in the front and back yard. Did I mention the big back yard? Endless possibilities, Come see this beauty for your self!
